title: SET_PLAYER_ROUTING_BUCKET
content:
0x6504EB38// SetPlayerRoutingBucket
void SET_PLAYER_ROUTING_BUCKET(char* playerSrc, int bucket);Parameters:playerSrc: The player to set the routing bucket for.bucket: The bucket ID.Sets the routing bucket for the specified player.Routing buckets are also known as 'dimensions' or 'virtual worlds' in past echoes, however they are population-aware.
